rows.label: fev11_330_150_msg0003
rows.name:
...I've never seen Adel like
that before.

rows.label: fev11_330_150_msg0004
rows.name:
He's gone off somewhere...
Is it best to leave him alone,
do you think?

rows.label: fev11_330_150_msg0005
rows.name:
That's for you to decide. I'll go where
you go.

rows.label: fev11_330_150_msg0007
rows.name:
No, he might need someone at a time
like this. We have to go after him.
